attempts.sparql_query: PREFIX atm: <https://data.nasa.gov/ontologies/atmonto/ATM#> PREFIX nas: <https://data.nasa.gov/ontologies/atmonto/NAS#> SELECT?country1?country2 WHERE { atm:AAL1170-201407150053 atm:departureAirport?dep1.?dep1 nas:locatedInState?state1.?state1 nas:locatedInCountry?country1. atm:ASQ3831-201407150019 atm:departureAirport?dep2.?dep2 nas:locatedInState?state2.?state2 nas:locatedInCountry?country2. }
attempts.query_explanation: This SPARQL query retrieves the countries of the departure airports of flights AAL1170 and ASQ3831. It does this by first finding the departure airports of the two flights, then finding the states in which these airports are located, and finally finding the countries in which these states are located. The query returns the countries of the departure airports of the two flights.
